73:All tasks dispatch via `task(subagent_type="general")`. Standard context: `{ issue_number, github.owner, github.repo, authorization_scope, halt_at, pr_strategy }`. `screen-issue` receives issue body + authorization context. `pre-implementation-analysis` receives all issue numbers + authorization context. `pre-analysis` receives only `{ issue_number, task_description }` with zero file paths. No inline work—all tasks dispatch sub-agents. Result contracts return `status` (DONE/BLOCKED/DONE_WITH_CONCERNS/OVERFLOW) + task-specific fields per `enforcement/` result contract schemas.
